quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  15,16,"Ke Rona ba thalehileng maholimo ka Mats’oao a Linaleli, Ra le ntlafatsa sebakeng sa babohi"
  15,17,Re A ts’irelelitse malebana le meea eohle ea liabolosi e lits’ila
  15,18,"Empa ea fumanang kutlo ka bokhukhuni, o salangoe ke khanare ea lelakabe"
  15,19,"Haele lefats’e lona re le alile joaloka moseme, eaba re beha holim’a lona Lithaba tse tsepameng ka tieo; le hona ho hlahisa lintho tsohle tsa mefuta holim’a lona ka tekano"
  15,20,Re le nehile boipheliso holim’a lona ekasitana le bao uena o sa ba fepeng letho
  15,21,Ha ho letho le teng leo mehloli ea lona e seng ho Rona. Ha Re romelle letho lefats’eng haese ka tekanyo e lekaneng
  15,22,"Re bile Re romella liphefo tse matlafatsang, le hona ho nesa pula e tsoang marung ho le neha metsi. Empa le se balebeli ba mehloli eo"
  15,23,"Ruri! Ke Rona ba fanang ka bophelo, le ho fana ka lefu, ke Rona ba salang E le majalefa"
  15,24,Ruri Re’a tseba ka ba potlakelang pele har’a lona le ba le le sisitheho
  15,25,"Bona! Mong`a hau U tla ba khobokanya ‘moho. Hobane Ruri U Seli, U hlokolosi"